FBIS4-48120 "drafr092_c_94016" FBIS-AFR-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Police Report Theft of Explosives at Bronkhorstspruit Police Report Theft of Explosives at Bronkhorstspruit MB1105184694 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 1500 GMT 11 May 94 MB1105184694 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network English BFN [Text] The police have embarked on a massive search after the theft of a large quantity of explosives from a factory at Bronkhorstspruit. A 50,000-rand reward has been offered for information leading to arrests in connection with the theft. The police have not commented on the possibility of right-wing involvement in the incident.
